Functional Requirements:



Payment Processing:
Users should be able to add payment methods securely.
Users should be able to make payments for event bookings.
The system should support various payment options such as credit/debit cards, net banking, wallets, etc.

Notifications:
-Users should receive email or SMS notifications for booking confirmations, cancellations, event reminders, etc.
-Users should be able to opt-in or opt-out of notifications.


Non-functional Requirements
